{"tid":1966634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(好撚大怨氣)有冇人屋企傢俬擺放好有問題","createTime":"2020-04-10T10:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T15:25:15.000Z","uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"76936f624b2fdbf8f338b94fa9dd297d02c04798","tid":1966634,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"屋企係兩房一廳細屋<br />\n本來屋企細應該更加要善用空間, 但係父母既LOGIC真係令我O嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買新傢俬之前已經講左電視要點放, 乜野舊傢俬要掉<br />\n買完返黎又係按照返佢地意思<br />\n<br />\n最後傢俬位置係:<br />\n下面條線=電視<br />\n-----<br />\n     -<br />\n     -   左邊係倒轉L型既沙發<br />\n-----<br />\n屌你咁撚樣買個沙發返黎拖柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全係亂尻咁黎, 然後係唔掉舊傢俬既情況下買張6人枱 (屋企只有4人, 平時屋企冇客人)<br />\n所有傢俬佔左成個廳既7成位置, 只有一條路俾人行<br />\n<br />\n同佢地講又唔聽, 間屋佢地既我完全冇話事權, 除非自己搬出去住<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係細唔係問題, 你唔好搞到成間屋好唔MAKE SENSE先得架<br />\n而家完全成間屋就係亂尻咁黎, 有女都唔敢帶返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9efed8fa005c5688cf7e06eb77195df9c345cd","tid":1966634,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"你講咁多嘢，直接講最後一句咪得<br />\n有錢咪搬出去lor"},{"pid":"8ffb58e95db21829682d33ea5ab74a73f7f68e8d","tid":1966634,"uid":40750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"我建議樓主你畫圖，屋企設計我老豆老母都好撚有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ab58fb2e5a0e5557c162c455d40e410809042e","tid":1966634,"uid":72045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a9efed8fa005c5688cf7e06eb77195df9c345cd","tid":1966634,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:20:36.00